| `backend/app/domain/astrology/runtime/aspect_calculation_contracts.py` / `AspectDefinitionRuntimeData` | `default_valence`, `interpretive_valence`, `energy_type` | Contrat legacy de transition qui expose des vues separees. | Temporary; sortie apres suppression dediee du contrat legacy. |
| `backend/app/domain/astrology/runtime/aspect_runtime_data.py` / `AspectInterpretationRuntimeData` | `default_valence`, `interpretive_valence`, `energy_type` | Projection legacy bornee d'indices interpretatifs. | Temporary; sortie apres migration des consommateurs legacy. |
